	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was bored and thought I'd draw something, but it ended up being a major pain in the ass. The way I made it is I made the font on the bottom, deleted the white in it, and then put it over the pattern in the top right. I'm not completely satisfied, but I think it looks good enough. I don't think I've actually seen any game have a gradient like that on the text, the closest I can think of is SF2 that has the gradient going diagonal. I could have made the gradient go out in a better circle, but it looked really awkward in spots. I didn't actually modify anything after laying it.<br /><br /><div class="attachtitle">Attachment:</div><div class="attachcontent">
			<img src="./download/file.php?id=6597" alt="Text.png" /><br />
			<span class="gensmall">Text.png [ 2.41 KiB | Viewed 3500 times ]</span>
		

		<br />
	</div><br />Man, if every aspect of what I'm trying to make has as much effort put into something as unimportant as the font, I'll end up making the best game ever. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif" alt=":lol:" title="Laughing" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
