		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, I had been told to put art related stuff here, even if it is for the SNES. Really, this (as well as just about anything else) is for any system that's capable enough to reasonably display it.<br /><br />I think I found out why I didn't really like what I had done: The color ramp is too long. I got rid of the second closest color to white and replaced it with white, and then I adjusted the middle color to where it is a little closer to the color above it than below it in terms of brightness. I think this is much better:<br /><br /><div class="attachtitle">Attachment:</div><div class="attachcontent">
