	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Against a black background the darker parts of the shading are a little hard to read.<br /><br />Also, characters with descenders ('p', 'g') look really weird and unbalanced here (see: &quot;happen&quot;, &quot;night&quot;) because they're too tall. Those are notoriously hard to get right but I think you could improve them here.

		

